<h2>Bulls and Cows Game Description</h2>

<p>
    Welcome to <strong>Bulls and Cows</strong>, a classic number guessing game! Your objective is to guess the secret <strong>4-digit</strong> number generated by the program in the fewest possible turns.
</p>

<h3>Game Rules:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>The secret number consists of exactly <strong>4 digits</strong>.</li>
    <li>All digits in the number must be <strong>unique</strong> (no repeating digits).</li>
    <li>The number cannot start with <strong>0</strong>.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Each turn, you will enter a 4-digit guess. The program will then compare your guess with the secret number and provide feedback in terms of bulls and cows.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>A "<span class="bull">bull</span>" <span class="icon">🐂</span> indicates that one of the entered digits is correct and in the right position.</li>
    <li>A "<span class="cow">cow</span>" <span class="icon">🐄</span> indicates that one of the entered digits is correct but in the wrong position.</li>
</ul>

