</p>

<h3>How to Play:</h3>

<p>
    To start playing enter any digit. Once you have entered a complete 4-digit number, press the <strong>Guess</strong> button.
    Analyze the results provided by the game and repeat this process until you find the correct number.
</p>

<p><strong>Tip:</strong> You can use different symbols to mark your guessed numbers in your list, such as 'x', '?', '✔', '1', '2', '3', '4' to help you keep track of your guesses.</p>

